#0300
<PRI<MSGA journal entry is on-screen.<NOD
Read it?<YNJ0000<CLR<TUR
January 12, 2417<NOD<CLR
Production is going well.<NOD<CLRUsing the strange flowers that
grow on this island, we've been
able to produce new medicines.<NOD<CLRThe creatures here that call
themselves the mimiga seem to have
an allergic reaction, however.<NOD<CLR
January 18, 2417<NOD<CLRWe have determined the cause of
the allergies is the reddish
flowers that grow here.<NOD<CLRMedicines that contain these
flowers have also had a large array
of negative side effects in humans.<NOD<CLRProduction of red medicines
has ceased, until we can properly
measure a counteragent.<NOD<CLR
January 26, 2417<NOD<CLR
There was an accident today.<NOD<CLROne of the mimiga children
managed to avoid detection and
found their way into the vault.<NOD<CLRIt ate copious amounts of the
red flowers we had locked away.
The child became violent and feral.<NOD<CLRTranquilizers had little to no
effect on the child. We had no
choice but to neutralize it.<NOD<CLO<MSG
The journal ends here...<NOD<END
#0301
<PRI<MSGA journal entry is on-screen.<NOD
Read it?<YNJ0000<CLR<TUR
February 3, 2417<NOD<CLRNegotiations with the mimiga
are at an all-time low.<NOD<CLRDespite our best efforts, the accident
with one of their children has led them
to believe we were at fault.<NOD<CLRThere is little doubt in my
mind that we truly are.<NOD<CLRI fear that child's curiosity
may have sparked a civil war between
humans and mimiga.<NOD<CLR
February 9, 2417<NOD<CLR
Higher-ups have doubled security today.<NOD<CLRMany of my co-workers feel uneasy
about the increase in security drones.
I too am stressed by this.<NOD<CLRI can do nothing but watch.
I have a horrible feeling of what
will come next.<NOD<CLR
February 12, 2417<NOD<CLRA security drone shot and killed a mimiga
on sight today. I do not know if it was
intentional, or a bug in its programming.<NOD<CLRMy fears are slowly confirming
themselves. I have applied for leave
immediately.<NOD<CLR
February 15, 2417<NOD<CLR
Still no response on my application.<NOD<CLRWhat are the higher-ups doing?
Are my associates and I merely
expendable resources?<NOD<CLR
February 19, 2417<NOD<CLRMy fears are all too true now.
The mimiga have gotten more and more
hostile towards humans.<NOD<CLROne attacked and bit a member of
security. It was immediately
neutralized.<NOD<CLRI can do nothing but watch.
I want to leave this place before
it spirals out of control.<NOD<CLO<MSG
The journal ends here...<NOD<END
#0302
<PRI<MSGA journal entry is on-screen.<NOD
Read it?<YNJ0000<CLR<TUR
February 28, 2417<NOD<CLRIt has been a month since my
application to leave, and still no
reply. I am trapped here.<NOD<CLRSecurity robots swarm the facility.
We can hardly do research around
them, there are so many.<NOD<CLR
I just want to return home.<NOD<CLR
March 6, 2417<NOD<CLRThe mimiga have broken into the vault,
and taken the red flowers and medicines
for themselves.<NOD<CLRSecurity is at an all-time high,
and morale is at an all-time low.<NOD<CLRThere are rumors going around that
they will begin 'pushing back' against
the mimiga.<NOD<CLR
They have done nothing wrong here.<NOD<CLRWho is in charge of this operation,
and why are they so desperate to
start a war between species?<NOD<CLR
March 13, 2417<NOD<CLR
Something horrible is amiss.<NOD<CLRThere are more and more reports of
security robots going rogue and
attacking both man and mimiga alike.<NOD<CLRMy heart is filled with so much
sorrow and worry, I can hardly
sleep a full night's worth.<NOD<CLRI have filed requests to leave almost
once a week now, since late February.
When will I ever leave this place?<NOD<CLR
March 20, 2417<NOD<CLR
They have started a full-on war.<NOD<CLRI have been reassigned from research
to hands-on medicine work. Men and women,
and mimiga alike are beaten and bloody.<NOD<CLR
I can do nothing but watch, and hope.<NOD<CLR
March 25, 2417<NOD<CLRThey have brought in weapons from off
the island that they gleefully nickname
"Deconstructor" Mk.1 and Mk.2.<NOD<CLRI tried to force myself onto the
transport before it left, but I was
apprehended, and told I'm needed here.<NOD<CLR
I pray for help.<NOD<CLR
March 31, 2417<NOD<CLR
They've turned on us now.<NOD<CLRSecurity robots everywhere, some
trustworthy, others fiendish. They don't
care if we're man or mimiga anymore.<NOD<CLR
Why is this happening?<NOD<CLR
April 2, 2417<NOD<CLR
I've managed to stop the bleeding.<NOD<CLRI don't have much time left.
If anyone's still alive, and they read
this journal...<NOD<CLR
Deconstructor Mk.2 has gone rogue.<NOD<CLR
Leave before it;d rik kcsn...<NOD<CLO<MSG
The journal ends here...<NOD<END
